1. Create parent pom
d:\workspace\APM5\Testapp>mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.quest.apm.testjavaee -DartifactId=APMTestJavaEE -DarchetypeGroupId=org.codehaus.mojo.archetypes -DarchetypeArtifactId=pom-root

2. Create EJB module
d:\workspace\APM5\Testapp\APMTestJavaEE>mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.quest.apm.testjavaee.ejb -DartifactId=ejb -DarchetypeGroupId=org.codehaus.mojo.archetypes -DarchetypeArtifactId=ejb-javaee6

3. Create Web module
d:\workspace\APM5\Testapp\APMTestJavaEE>mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.quest.apm.testjavaee.web -DartifactId=war -DarchetypeGroupId=org.codehaus.mojo.archetypes -DarchetypeArtifactId=webapp-javaee6

4. Create Ear module
d:\workspace\APM5\Testapp\APMTestJavaEE>mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.quest.apm.testjavaee -DartifactId=ear -DarchetypeGroupId=org.codehaus.mojo.archetypes -DarchetypeArtifactId=ear-javaee6

Genarate idea project files
mvn idea:idea

Build and install the packages:
mvn install